{"tid":2183327,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美「太子站」承載心痛憤怒  加300人高呼：失蹤港人安息","createTime":"2020-09-01T01:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T01:22:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25143194442ef492fc2d6f499833cde4a6882935","tid":2183327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/PDB5BF6IKJFCXFCWTZDQSVH76M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FPDB5BF6IKJFCXFCWTZDQSVH76M%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7gz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=18ce5712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FPDB5BF6IKJFCXFCWTZDQSVH76M%2F&h=cfe976d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/PDB5BF6IKJFCXFCWTZDQSVH76M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美「太子站」承載心痛憤怒 <br />\n加300人高呼：失蹤港人安息<br />\n<br />\n【紀念港殤】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台三地築人鏈 流亡手足撐港<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一年前的8.31太子站襲擊在香港人心內留下難以磨滅的烙印。美國和加拿大的華人組織前日下午分別舉辦悼念活動，其中在美國的組織更製作港鐵「太子站」模型，有民眾獻花悼念，希望推動海外力量繼續支持香港人。<br />\n<br />\n紐約華人組織「NY4HK」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紐約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eHm9oqse1J85Cv3ytJgKx-_BmpI=/2363x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VUJ2FLXYIBEJNGYWZPHYQGMESM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeHm9oqse1J85Cv3ytJgKx-_BmpI%3D%2F2363x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVUJ2FLXYIBEJNGYWZPHYQGMESM.jpg&h=f07ac650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紐約 ■華人組織「NY4HK」在聯合廣場公園砌起「太子站」模型，眾人身穿黑衣到場悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「威權一方試圖亂寫歷史」<br />\n<br />\n「NY4HK」其中一名負責人表示：「在中國不能講六四，在香港就不能講8.31。威權一方試圖亂寫歷史 ，但香港人會將真相完全記錄下來。雖然將來所有產品都只能標籤『Made in China』，但香港人人格永遠都係『Made in Hong Kong 』。」<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，8.31當日只能透過網上直播和新聞報道了解事件，感受到很大的無力感」，也曾覺得十分沮喪。雖然疫情肆虐加上港版國安法生效，很多在美港人都認為難以再親身回港支持抗爭運動，但他們會堅持信念，推動海外力量繼續支持香港人。<br />\n<br />\n「三藩市香港人公海」在三藩市鄰近城市紅木城舉行了一場8.31悼念活動， 約90人參加。團隊以「同氣連根，分苦共甘」鼓勵香港人，無論他們身在地球何地，都不會忘記自己是香港人的身份，繼續與香港人同行。<br />\n<br />\n團隊特別為8.31悼念活動製作了一個六呎高的立體太子站模型， 眾人高舉白色摺花默哀，並排隊到站前獻花。會上有參加者分享對8.31的感受，指當時看見直播及流出手機片段時，既心痛亦憤怒。活動由八人各高舉一塊白紙板走到廣場站立開始，眾人亦手持白紙加入， 藉此吸引途人駐足閱讀團隊預備的文宣。 有當地市民詢問及希望了解香港情況， 也有市民直接前來表達對香港的支持及關注。<br />\n<br />\n集會中有一抗爭活動回顧環節，主持先敍述抗爭事件， 眾人一邊揮動「光時」旗幟，一邊高呼所有由上年6月至今香港人高呼過的口號。 參加者由「香港人加油」、「沒有暴徒， 只有暴政」、「五大訴求， 缺一不可」等一直回顧香港發生的大事，直到今年7月港版國安法，港人已刻下「光復香港，時代革命」的決心作結 。活動最後以寄明信片到不同參眾兩院議員作結， 旨在對議員表達他們早前通過香港人權法的感激之情，以及希望在復會後他們可以通過更多幫助香港人的法案。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大香港聯盟在溫哥華發起「失蹤港人安息，提供安全庇護」的抗議活動，約300人參與，。。。。。。。。。。。，路過的汽車不時響號支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三藩市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-og8hu47SJeuN64Goz8922n0uYY=/1769x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XHI2XE4EBJB63A74HP2IKRDSQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-og8hu47SJeuN64Goz8922n0uYY%3D%2F1769x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXHI2XE4EBJB63A74HP2IKRDSQA.jpg&h=be4a0928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三藩市 ■參加者高舉白紙在廣場站立，藉此吸引途人駐足閱讀有關香港抗爭的文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_R8I66rA_ngfgDhvaGUduwloinY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UZIKLO2ED5F7BGYTZTKRPSFOZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_R8I66rA_ngfgDhvaGUduwloinY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUZIKLO2ED5F7BGYTZTKRPSFOZU.jpg&h=1037c37c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參加者手持文宣呼籲毋忘8.31太子站事件。<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf93f7b0b9e08c581af37db9face2a337f9cf3cc","tid":2183327,"uid":176313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"沉冤未雪，如何安息&hellip;<br />\n香港人，繼續做嘢！"},{"pid":"43122b2a809900beb3d2ee3cf35397654e06ae99","tid":2183327,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:15:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">毒果至撚中意報隔岸觀火啦啦隊大Party，抗爭？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"910b6a5fe88f5eb5b7a91850fd3e068d63fca71b","tid":2183327,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fe555d74d14d4d7888feaedeaa840da701789d","tid":2183327,"uid":245544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:16:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"057ee35f19abfaa79bffa36202601a4d810d662d","tid":2183327,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfba993a13cbf7eea2e576f311b7ceea71739342","tid":2183327,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e9f3242f9e5c0fdd4cd802cdda4f210167c